# SMTP API Service

A simple SMTP API service that provides email sending capabilities via REST API.

## Getting Started

### Prerequisites
- Go 1.16 or higher
- SMTP server credentials

### Develompent

 1. Clone Github repository
  ```git clone [text](https://github.com/tantojos4/smtpapi-go.git)```
   ** make sure golang installing your computer
2. Installing Dependencies
    ```go mod tidy```
3. Run Development
    ```go run main.go```
4. Request true no validation error
    ```curl -X POST http://localhost:8080/send-email \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{
    "to": "recipient@example.com",
    "from": "sender@example.com",
    "subject": "Test Email",
    "body": "This is a test email"
  }'```
5. Request false 
  ```curl -X POST http://localhost:8080/send-email \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{
    "to": "bukan-email",
    "from": "sender@example.com",
    "subject": "",
    "body": ""
  }'```
